n","tg/election"],"."]]]," sure: for if ye do these things, ye shall never ",["fall",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 50:44","dc-testament/dc/50.44"],"."]]],":"]],[11,["For so an entrance shall be ministered unto you abundantly into the ",["everlasting",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Immortality","tg/immortality"],"."]]]," ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Kingdom of God, on Earth","tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"],"."]]]," of our Lord and Saviour Jesus Christ."]],[12,["Wherefore I will not be negligent to put you always in remembrance of these things, though ye know ",["them,",["clarity-word"]]," and be established in the present truth."]],[13,["Yea, I think it ",["meet",["study-note-ref","a",["GR right, just, righteous."]]],", as long as I am in this ",["tabernacle",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 93:4, 35","dc-testament/dc/93.4,35"],"."]]],", to stir you up by putting ",["you",["clarity-word"]]," in remembrance;"]],[14,["Knowing that shortly I must put off ",["this",["clarity-word"]]," my tabernacle, even as our Lord Jesus Christ hath ",["shewed",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 21:19 (18–19)","nt/john/21.19"],"."]]]," me."]],[15,["Moreover I will endeavour that ye may be able after my decease to ",["",1552],"have these things always in remembrance."]],[16,["For we have not followed cunningly devised ",["fables",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Tim. 1:4","nt/1-tim/1.4"],"."]]],", when we made known unto you the power and coming of our Lord Jesus Christ, but were ",["eyewitnesses",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 17:2 (1–9)","nt/matt/17.2"],"; ",["John 1:14","nt/john/1.14"],". ",["TG Witness","tg/witness"],"."]]]," of his majesty."]],[17,["For he received from God the Father honour and glory, when there came such a voice to him from the excellent glory, This is my ",["beloved Son",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Witness of the Father","tg/witness-of-the-father"],"."]]],", in whom I am well pleased."]],[18,["And this ",["voice",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],";